# Linux Security and Hardening  

repository contains material for course **Linux Security and Hardening**
  
# genutzte Distributionen
  
- [x] [Debian 12](https://www.debian.org/distrib/)
- [x] [Rocky Linux 9](https://rockylinux.org/download)
- [x] [OpenSuse 15](https://get.opensuse.org/)

# Quelle  
  
- Buch: [Mastering Linux Security and Hardening](https://amzn.eu/d/jeEpUA3) von Donald A. Tevault
- online unter: [packtpub.com](https://www.packtpub.com/)
- offline in 3rd edition: book_3rd_edition.pdf
  
